6-Mar. 22, 1907. Resumes numbering of The White Pine news (Treasure City, Nev. : 1868) in 1909. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Issued also in weekly edition: White Pine news weekly mining review (1907), Jan. 12, 1907-Dec. 14, 1907; White Pine news weekly mining review (1909), Jan. 2, 1909-February 19, 1910. White Pine news weekly mining review (East Ely, Nev. : 1910) 2771-8123 (DLC)sn 86076354 (OCoLC)14066797"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:05.071Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-11", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-11"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [39.253136, -114.875111], "location": ["white pine", "united states", "ely", "nevada"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-114.875111, 39.253136], "number": ["original", "sn86076354", "sn86076249", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/1906-12-25/ed-1/", "nevada state museum & historical society", "1083", "sn84022047", "sn86076355", "online resource", "2025-07-01t13:40:36.900000", "sn86076357", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/1910-06-30/ed-1/", "1", "2023-06-27t19:21:13.388758", "2771-5515", "13790203", "univ of nevada, las vegas", "microfilm service copy"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Daily White Pine news", "White Pine daily news", "White Pine news daily edition and weekly mining review", "White Pine news Saturday edition", "White Pine weekly news"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the white pine news (ely, nev.) 1906-1910", "serial and government publications division", "catalog"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 65.17704, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["ely", "ely (